video.title: Resurrection: Ertugrul
video.synopsis: When a good deed unwittingly endangers his clan, a 13th-century Turkish warrior agrees to fight a sultan's enemies in exchange for new tribal land.

episodes.synopsis: Winter approaches Süleyman Shah's camp. On a hunt, Ertuğrul rescues prisoners from the Crusaders. Commander Titus and Üstadı Azam build a new army.
episodes.title: Episode 1

episodes.synopsis: Kara Toygar threatens the Kayı camp when Süleyman Shah refuses to turn over the prisoners. Titus learns the excruciating truth about his brother.
episodes.title: Episode 2

episodes.synopsis: In the search for a new camp, Süleyman sends Ertuğrul to Aleppo and fuels fraternal jealousy. Kurdoğlu makes a deal with Kara Toygar.
episodes.title: Episode 3

episodes.synopsis: On the way to Aleppo, a dangerous enemy crosses paths with Ertuğrul. Halime and her family come under attack.
episodes.title: Episode 4

episodes.synopsis: Fate hands Titus a golden chance for revenge, but the timing is not right. Selcan conspires with Gökçe to boost their status in the family.
episodes.title: Episode 5

episodes.synopsis: A premonition saves Ertuğrul's life as Titus raises the stakes against him. Üstadı Azam turns up the heat on his rivals.
episodes.title: Episode 6

episodes.synopsis: Süleyman's prayers are answered, but Gündoğdu's life hangs by a thread. Kurdoğlu puts another plan into action.
episodes.title: Episode 7

episodes.synopsis: A mysterious messenger puts a damper on the Kayı tribe's festivities. Süleyman presses Halime's father about his true identity.
episodes.title: Episode 8

episodes.synopsis: Sensing imminent danger, Şehzade Numan asks Süleyman for a favor. Süleyman shows Kara Toygar that he has the upper hand -- but not for long.
episodes.title: Episode 9

episodes.synopsis: The prisoner exchange goes awry. At the camp, Hayme stands up to Kurdoğlu, who exploits another opportunity to strike against Süleyman.
episodes.title: Episode 10

episodes.synopsis: Kurdoğlu puts his plan in motion, but Ertuğrul is one step ahead of him. Selcan tries to turn the tables in her favor.
episodes.title: Episode 11

episodes.synopsis: Kurdoğlu intervenes on behalf of Kara Toygar. Selcan's maneuvering pays off, but Gündoğdu spoils everything.
episodes.title: Episode 12

episodes.synopsis: On the way to Aleppo, Ertuğrul and Halime walk into the lion's den. Gündoğdu and Kurdoğlu have a heated faceoff.
episodes.title: Episode 13

episodes.synopsis: Üstadı Azam is determined to eliminate anyone who stands in the way of his campaign. Süleyman's greatest threat is close by.
episodes.title: Episode 14

episodes.synopsis: Selcan tries to kill two birds with one stone, but her ambition becomes her downfall. With Halime in critical condition, Ertuğrul's group splits up.
episodes.title: Episode 15

episodes.synopsis: Üstadı Azam uses İbn Arabi to tighten the screws on Giovanni. An informant pulls the wool over Şahabettin's eyes.
episodes.title: Episode 16

episodes.synopsis: Şahabettin falls deeper into love's trap. The Knights Templar's lethal weapon strikes the Kayı tribe on the eve of their migration.
episodes.title: Episode 17

episodes.synopsis: Şahabettin is key to Ertuğrul's plan, but El Aziz stands in the way. Turgut and Yiğit are still missing, but Ertuğrul has a more immediate problem.
episodes.title: Episode 18

episodes.synopsis: After narrowly escaping a tragic fate, Ertuğrul makes a radical plan as time runs out for Şahabettin.
episodes.title: Episode 19

episodes.synopsis: With El Aziz unwavering in his decision, Şahabettin prepares to embrace his fate, but a hooded stranger makes a surprise showing.
episodes.title: Episode 20

episodes.synopsis: Izadora takes Yiğit under her wing. Nasır has El Aziz wrapped around his finger and orders a thorough manhunt to finish what he started.
episodes.title: Episode 21

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul cautions Numan, who puts himself in the firing line at El Aziz's palace. A visitor gives Turgut hope.
episodes.title: Episode 22

episodes.synopsis: Deli Demir heads for Aleppo and cannot believe what he sees upon arrival. Ertuğrul puts his life on the line to set a trap for Nasır.
episodes.title: Episode 23

episodes.synopsis: Titus brushes up against a sworn enemy from the past. During a confrontation with Nasır, Ertuğrul faces a difficult choice.
episodes.title: Episode 24

episodes.synopsis: Leyla helps Ertuğrul at a critical moment, but her absence draws attention. Seeking answers about her family, Izadora makes a deal with Turgut.
episodes.title: Episode 25

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul makes a narrow escape. Nasır has an elaborate plan for Halime, who struggles to make El Aziz see the truth.
episodes.title: Episode 26

episodes.synopsis: Aykız takes matters into her own hands and pays Eftelya a visit. Üstadı Azam goes after a mole on his own turf.
episodes.title: Episode 27

episodes.synopsis: Gündoğdu and Selcan come to blows over her ambitions. Ertuğrul brings pressure to bear on Eftelya, but the tribe needs her alive.
episodes.title: Episode 28

episodes.synopsis: To infiltrate the Knights Templar's base, Ertuğrul deliberately leaks information. Numan's decision deals a major blow to Halime.
episodes.title: Episode 29

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul captures an important prisoner on the way. Üstadı Azam grooms Yiğit for the final stage of his plan.
episodes.title: Episode 30

episodes.synopsis: A message arrives at the Kayı camp, and Selcan decides it is time to settle accounts with Süleyman. Marcus falls for the Kayı tribe's ruse.
episodes.title: Episode 31

episodes.synopsis: Titus wreaks havoc on the camp. A surprise visitor knocks on Afşin's door, and Numan leaves Ertuğrul no choice but to walk away from Halime.
episodes.title: Episode 32

episodes.synopsis: As Titus's plan spirals out of control and he and Kurdoğlu look for a way out, Şahabettin watches them closely.
episodes.title: Episode 33

episodes.synopsis: The Knights Templar's position in Aleppo depends on Eftelya, who tries to turn Ertuğrul against Halime.
episodes.title: Episode 34

episodes.synopsis: Eftelya decides her own fate. A showdown between Ertuğrul and Titus gets interrupted, and Ertuğrul questions Kara Toygar's true motives.
episodes.title: Episode 35

episodes.synopsis: Nasır oversteps his bounds with El Aziz, and Halime seizes her chance to appeal on behalf of the Kayı tribe.
episodes.title: Episode 36

episodes.synopsis: In pitting herself against Selcan, Aykız plays with fire. Ertuğrul rushes to head off the diplomatic mess Nasır created.
episodes.title: Episode 37

episodes.synopsis: Selcan falls out of Hayme's favor. Ertuğrul walks into an important meeting and exposes a conspiracy against his tribe.
episodes.title: Episode 38

episodes.synopsis: El Aziz hands down a harsh sentence to Leyla and Nanny. Ertuğrul and Gündoğdu return home to a slew of shocking news.
episodes.title: Episode 39

episodes.synopsis: News about Halime sends Ertuğrul back on the road. Claudius accepts a mission that puts İbn Arabi in harm's way.
episodes.title: Episode 40

episodes.synopsis: Kurdoğlu tries to turn Süleyman and Gündoğdu against Ertuğrul, who negotiates with El Aziz at knifepoint.
episodes.title: Episode 41

episodes.synopsis: Üstadı Azam loses his grip on Aleppo. At the camp, public opinion is not in Süleyman's favor, and Hayme cracks down on Selcan.
episodes.title: Episode 42

episodes.synopsis: Claudius's mission hits a snag. Hayme discovers that Selcan has a personal vendetta, but Gündoğdu stands by Selcan.
episodes.title: Episode 43

episodes.synopsis: Gündoğdu unwittingly becomes a part of Kurdoğlu's scheme. Hayme gives Halime and Gökçe a dilemma.
episodes.title: Episode 44

episodes.synopsis: Gündoğdu squares off with Ertuğrul. Selcan stirs the pot at the family meal, where an unexpected guest arrives with distressing news for Halime.
episodes.title: Episode 45

episodes.synopsis: Cardinal Thomas and Titus carry out their plan with Turgut, whose decisions spell disaster for Ertuğrul.
episodes.title: Episode 46

episodes.synopsis: Süleyman meets with the Seljuks, but Ertuğrul's return throws the camp into disarray. Halime refuses the Seljuk sultan's offer.
episodes.title: Episode 47

episodes.synopsis: With their greatest obstacle out of the way, Üstadı Azam and Kurdoğlu advance on their target, but Gündoğdu tests Kurdoğlu's loyalty.
episodes.title: Episode 48

episodes.synopsis: A visitor brings news of Turgut to the Kayı camp and puts Kurdoğlu in an unfavorable position. A murder plot unravels.
episodes.title: Episode 49

episodes.synopsis: Kurdoğlu incurs Selcan's wrath. Izadora helps Süleyman connect the dots, and Eftelya gets her hands on an important letter.
episodes.title: Episode 50

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul and Süleyman put Kurdoğlu on the stand, but Gündoğdu steps in. Thomas tests Üstadı Azam's patience.
episodes.title: Episode 51

episodes.synopsis: Turgut is not out of the woods yet. Selcan pulls strings to influence Gündoğdu, and Hayme loses control of the situation.
episodes.title: Episode 52

episodes.synopsis: Gökçe overhears Selcan's secret plan, and Süleyman invites a contest for power that threatens to pit his sons against each other.
episodes.title: Episode 53

episodes.synopsis: Gökçe sees Selcan's true colors and confronts her. Gündoğdu plays into Kurdoğlu's hands, but someone more powerful has a hidden plan.
episodes.title: Episode 54

episodes.synopsis: Selcan loses favor with Gündoğdu as her ambitions get the best of her. Kurdoğlu unleashes another weapon to sow chaos in the camp.
episodes.title: Episode 55

episodes.synopsis: While Süleyman gives him the benefit of the doubt, Kurdoğlu misleads Süleyman's men. Yiğit's life is in enemy hands.
episodes.title: Episode 56

episodes.synopsis: After losing their only witness, Ertuğrul and his men are back to square one on the hunt for the traitor, but Izadora gives them another lead.
episodes.title: Episode 57

episodes.synopsis: Kurdoğlu takes advantage of Ertuğrul's absence. When the Knights Templar outnumber Ertuğrul, his wit is the only thing that can save him.
episodes.title: Episode 58

episodes.synopsis: Kurdoğlu tries to force Selcan's hand and makes Turgut his right-hand man. Ertuğrul has valuable information that Üstadı Azam needs.
episodes.title: Episode 59

episodes.synopsis: Struggling to keep order among his subjects, Kurdoğlu hands down Süleyman's sentence and sets a dangerous trap for him and Hayme.
episodes.title: Episode 60

episodes.synopsis: Selcan repents and decides to mend fences with those she has betrayed. Ertuğrul meets an unlikely ally.
episodes.title: Episode 61

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul prepares to settle accounts with Kurdoğlu, who is suspicious of Ayhan's loyalties. The Kayı tribe's fate depends on Turgut.
episodes.title: Episode 62

episodes.synopsis: The Knights Templar's plan comes apart at the seams, and Izadora pays a price. Claudius causes a rift between Thomas and Üstadı Azam.
episodes.title: Episode 63

episodes.synopsis: A confrontation between Ertuğrul and Kurdoğlu ends in bloodshed. With Üstadı Azam in grave condition, Thomas gains the upper hand.
episodes.title: Episode 64

episodes.synopsis: Kurdoğlu's judgment day arrives, but Thomas still has one advantage over the Kayı tribe. İbn Arabi convinces Selcan to change her ways.
episodes.title: Episode 65

episodes.synopsis: Titus is determined to eradicate the Kayı tribe. Claudius brings urgent news to Ertuğrul, who plans an offensive campaign into enemy territory.
episodes.title: Episode 66

episodes.synopsis: After Deli Demir and Afşin Bey find a way to infiltrate the Knights Templar, the Kayı tribe readies for battle.
episodes.title: Episode 67

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul's army catches the Knights Templar off guard. In a tight spot, Titus suspects there's an informant from within.
episodes.title: Episode 68

episodes.synopsis: Under Titus's watch, Ömer plays a risky double game. Selcan's sudden realization changes her fate.
episodes.title: Episode 69

episodes.synopsis: Ömer pays a heavy price for his betrayal. Yiğit helps to lead Ertuğrul and his army on the road to victory.
episodes.title: Episode 70

episodes.synopsis: Turgut gets his sweet revenge. With Titus still a threat to the Kayı army, Ertuğrul's men set out on a manhunt.
episodes.title: Episode 71

episodes.synopsis: Gündoğdu responds unexpectedly to Selcan's big news. At the Kayı camp, danger still lingers in the shadows.
episodes.title: Episode 72

episodes.synopsis: Selcan atones for her crimes and risks her life for Gündoğdu, who confronts a dangerous enemy from the past.
episodes.title: Episode 73

episodes.synopsis: İbn Arabi leaves Ertuğrul with a valuable relic. A perilous journey lies ahead for Ertuğrul and Süleyman.
episodes.title: Episode 74

episodes.synopsis: As Ertuğrul consolidates power across Anatolia, Hayme fears that an ominous premonition may come true.
episodes.title: Episode 75

episodes.synopsis: As the Kayı tribe struggles with its sudden loss, Hayme calls a meeting to form a strategy against new threats.
episodes.title: Episode 76

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul and Halime encounter new enemies, and sudden misfortune befalls the Kayı camp.
episodes.title: Episode 77

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul's fate is uncertain, and the Oğuz Turks swear to take revenge, but a shadowy figure watches them.
episodes.title: Episode 78

episodes.synopsis: Aytolun has her own ambitions. Gökçe overhears Halime break the big news to Hayme.
episodes.title: Episode 79

episodes.synopsis: Gündoğdu attempts to track down Noyan, while the Kayı tribe mourns two tragic losses.
episodes.title: Episode 80

episodes.synopsis: Selcan warns Gündoğdu about the alliance, as Aytolun plants ideas in Tuğtekin's head. Noyan turns up the heat on Ertuğrul.
episodes.title: Episode 81

episodes.synopsis: An informant lurks among the Turks, who mobilize for a new campaign. Aytolun sets her plan in motion and inquires after Gökçe.
episodes.title: Episode 82

episodes.synopsis: The Turks and Mongols play cat and mouse as Gündoğdu and Tuğtekin attempt to isolate the mole in their group.
episodes.title: Episode 83

episodes.synopsis: To solidify the alliance, Korkut Bey makes Hayme an offer. Aytolun learns something new about Gökçe that complicates her plan.
episodes.title: Episode 84

episodes.synopsis: Hayme's decision threatens to pit Selcan against Aytolun. Ertuğrul's disappearance leaves Noyan in a vulnerable position.
episodes.title: Episode 85

episodes.synopsis: Gündoğdu tries to get behind Noyan's motives, but the Kayı tribe's greatest threat lies within.
episodes.title: Episode 86

episodes.synopsis: Tuğtekin faces a new competitor and lets his ambitions get the best of him. Tensions escalate between the clans.
episodes.title: Episode 87

episodes.synopsis: Aytolun and Tuğtekin plot a power grab, and Ertuğrul's announcement leads to an important vote in the camp.
episodes.title: Episode 88

episodes.synopsis: The vote heightens tensions between the clans and sets Gökçe against Halime, as Selcan's warnings fall on deaf ears.
episodes.title: Episode 89

episodes.synopsis: Tuğtekin becomes fed up with Ertuğrul's lingering influence on the camp. Ertuğrul makes a separate plan with those still loyal to him.
episodes.title: Episode 90

episodes.synopsis: Noyan makes Gündoğdu his next target. Kocabaş's words instigate a confrontation that changes Ertuğrul's place in the camp.
episodes.title: Episode 91

episodes.synopsis: Tuğtekin intends to flex his muscles in front of Ertuğrul, and Gökçe decides to play a different game.
episodes.title: Episode 92

episodes.synopsis: Korkut Bey is haunted by his own demons. As Ertuğrul struggles to get back on his feet, mutiny lurks around the corner.
episodes.title: Episode 93

episodes.synopsis: Hamza's action leads to dire consequences for the Kayı tribe. With Abdurrahman's life on the line, Ertuğrul goes after a traitor.
episodes.title: Episode 94

episodes.synopsis: Hayme helps mend fences between Ertuğrul and Gündoğdu. Tuğtekin's tactics against Kayı subjects become harsher by the day.
episodes.title: Episode 95

episodes.synopsis: When the two clans face off over Abdurrahman's sentence, Gündoğdu makes Korkut Bey an offer and saves the day.
episodes.title: Episode 96

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul plans a ruse with Deli Demir's help and is forced to leave the camp, while an enemy lurks nearby.
episodes.title: Episode 97

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul experiences a close shave as Noyan's army draws dangerously close. Hayme takes matters into her own hands.
episodes.title: Episode 98

episodes.synopsis: Selcan tries to uncover what Aytolun is after, but Ertuğrul is one step ahead and sends his team on a mission back to the camp.
episodes.title: Episode 99

episodes.synopsis: Noyan tests Abdurrahman's loyalties. Hayme confronts Korkut Bey about Aytolun and Tuğtekin's behavior.
episodes.title: Episode 100

episodes.synopsis: Stunned by Hayme's announcement, Selcan tries to stop Gökçe from falling into Aytolun's trap, but Gökçe has not yet made up her mind.
episodes.title: Episode 101

episodes.synopsis: A surprise visitor traces Ertuğrul to his hidden refuge. Ertokuş Bey arrives at the camp with an important message for Ertuğrul.
episodes.title: Episode 102

episodes.synopsis: Abdurrahman talks himself out of a tragic end. Kocabaş attempts to get ahold of Ertokuş Bey's secret, but someone else overhears.
episodes.title: Episode 103

episodes.synopsis: Ertokuş checks Korkut Bey's ambitions, but Aytolun refuses to back down. Noyan's men corner Ertuğrul.
episodes.title: Episode 104

episodes.synopsis: Goncagül proves herself a force to be reckoned with. Gümüştekin Bey's sudden arrival turns the tables and divides the camp.
episodes.title: Episode 105

episodes.synopsis: Hayme stands up to Gümüştekin and gives the Dodurga clan an ultimatum. Gökçe eavesdrops on Halime.
episodes.title: Episode 106

episodes.synopsis: Artuk Bey encourages Korkut Bey to take charge. Gündoğdu becomes a pawn in two separate games of power.
episodes.title: Episode 107

episodes.synopsis: Hayme's courier carries out a risky task. After she sees a stranger accost Aytolun, Selcan digs into Aytolun's past.
episodes.title: Episode 108

episodes.synopsis: Selcan stands to pay dearly for what she discovers. Ertuğrul battles on two fronts, and Tuğtekin digs his own grave.
episodes.title: Episode 109

episodes.synopsis: Noyan plots to weaken the Kayı and Dodurga clans by dividing them. Aytolun and Goncagül's plan for Gündoğdu begins to take shape.
episodes.title: Episode 110

episodes.synopsis: Unfortunate news arrives, wreaking havoc on the camp. Aytolun grows desperate to stop Korkut Bey from acting on a rash decision against the Kayı clan.
episodes.title: Episode 111

episodes.synopsis: An orchestrated riot concludes unexpectedly when a visitor's sudden arrival at the camp leads to bloodshed.
episodes.title: Episode 112

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul brings news that may give the Kayı clan a second chance. As Hayme's condition remains uncertain, Selcan confronts Aytolun.
episodes.title: Episode 113

episodes.synopsis: Gümüştekin stands his ground in a negotiation over Ertuğrul's standing. A ruthless enemy is hot on Halime's tail.
episodes.title: Episode 114

episodes.synopsis: Gündoğdu gives Selcan an ultimatum. In a vulnerable position, Ertuğrul warns Gündoğdu about another infiltrator.
episodes.title: Episode 115

episodes.synopsis: Gündoğdu attempts to make Korkut Bey see the truth about recent treachery in the camp. Halime's pursuer catches her and Deli Demir unawares.
episodes.title: Episode 116

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul's day of reckoning is imminent. Halime's life hangs by a thread, but a veiled stranger comes to her rescue.
episodes.title: Episode 117

episodes.synopsis: Karabek brings in a witness during Ertuğrul's sentencing, and a battle of wills ensues between the two clans.
episodes.title: Episode 118

episodes.synopsis: Noyan's old rival makes a comeback. Gümüştekin's plan becomes a pipe dream, and Aytolun decides to resort to more desperate measures.
episodes.title: Episode 119

episodes.synopsis: Noyan plots a new scheme against the Kayı clan. As leadership changes in the camp, Tuğtekin refuses to give up on the power game.
episodes.title: Episode 120

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul grows suspicious of Noyan's true intentions toward Abdurrahman. Artuk takes Ertuğrul to an important gathering.
episodes.title: Episode 121

episodes.synopsis: Gümüştekin and Saadettin Köpek find a common target. Goncagül blackmails Selcan to keep her away from Gündoğdu.
episodes.title: Episode 122

episodes.synopsis: Hayme warns Gündoğdu about Gümüştekin's potential ambitions. Selcan reaches an impasse because of Goncagül.
episodes.title: Episode 123

episodes.synopsis: Sungur Tekin requests a meeting with Ertuğrul. Abdurrahman is in a precarious state, and Gündoğdu sets out on a new campaign.
episodes.title: Episode 124

episodes.synopsis: Sungur Tekin warns Ertuğrul about looming danger and hands him a valuable seal, but someone dangerous eavesdrops in the shadows.
episodes.title: Episode 125

episodes.synopsis: Goncagül steps up her charm offensive. Ertuğrul returns to the camp with unpleasant news for Hayme.
episodes.title: Episode 126

episodes.synopsis: Selcan searches desperately for an ally against Aytolun. Gümüştekin goes after something he believes to be in Sungur Tekin's possession.
episodes.title: Episode 127

episodes.synopsis: Selcan and Halime seek Doğan's help in convincing Banu Çiçek. Goncagül gets her hands on a sought-after item.
episodes.title: Episode 128

episodes.synopsis: Noyan's spies at the camp have an escape strategy, but Gündoğdu double-crosses them and defends his plan in front of Korkut Bey.
episodes.title: Episode 129

episodes.synopsis: Hamza's loyalties come under question. Using Selcan as his bargaining chip, Noyan presents Gündoğdu with a dilemma.
episodes.title: Episode 130

episodes.synopsis: Gökçe and Halime come to blows over Selcan. Noyan's demands give Aytolun and Goncagül an opportunity.
episodes.title: Episode 131

episodes.synopsis: The Kayı clan struggles to solve the mystery of the missing seal. Gündoğdu reveals his game to Noyan, but not without bloodshed.
episodes.title: Episode 132

episodes.synopsis: Gümüştekin holds on to a valuable possession and conspires with Aytolun, putting Korkut Bey's life on the line.
episodes.title: Episode 133

episodes.synopsis: A powerful new enemy gets wind of Ertuğrul's military endeavors. Goncagül's envy drives her to desperation.
episodes.title: Episode 134

episodes.synopsis: With Noyan's fate in enemy hands, Tangut decides to avenge himself. Halime sneaks into Aytolun's tent and risks getting caught red-handed.
episodes.title: Episode 135

episodes.synopsis: Halime suspects Banu Çiçek is hiding a secret. In a twist of fate for Noyan, Saadettin Köpek arrives to challenge the clans' decisions.
episodes.title: Episode 136

episodes.synopsis: Gümüştekin makes a deal with Saadettin Köpek that may imperil the Kayı clan, but he is unaware of Saadettin Köpek's hidden agenda.
episodes.title: Episode 137

episodes.synopsis: Defying the camp's vote, Sungur Tekin decides to seal Noyan's fate himself, and Saadettin Köpek takes on a risky gamble with Noyan.
episodes.title: Episode 138

episodes.synopsis: The Oğuz seal falls into the wrong hands, and Hayme calls Goncagül in for questioning. Sungur Tekin's mission comes at a cost.
episodes.title: Episode 139

episodes.synopsis: As the Kayı clan mourns its loss, Sungur Tekin derails Saadettin Köpek's plan, and Ertuğrul suspects intrigue.
episodes.title: Episode 140

episodes.synopsis: After a confrontation with Selcan, Banu Çiçek reconsiders her loyalty to Aytolun. Ertuğrul squares off with Gümüştekin.
episodes.title: Episode 141

episodes.synopsis: Gümüştekin uses Goncagül to manipulate Gündoğdu, and plans to frame Banu Çiçek in a scheme that may also endanger Aytolun.
episodes.title: Episode 142

episodes.synopsis: When the camp descends into chaos on Gökçe and Tuğtekin's big night, Gündoğdu discovers evidence in Korkut Bey's room.
episodes.title: Episode 143

episodes.synopsis: Selcan puts her own life at risk by telling the truth. Banu Çiçek convinces Ertuğrul to scrutinize the facts behind the poisoning.
episodes.title: Episode 144

episodes.synopsis: Determined to learn Aytolun's secret, Ertuğrul sends Doğan on a risky mission, and Banu Çiçek's survival is key to his plan.
episodes.title: Episode 145

episodes.synopsis: Gündoğdu is torn between Selcan and Goncagül. Ertuğrul prepares to fight fire with fire and makes another decision that may pit him against Gündoğdu.
episodes.title: Episode 146

episodes.synopsis: Goncagül pulls the wool over Gündoğdu's eyes and puts Selcan in a helpless position, but Ertuğrul has a hidden plan to expose the real killers.
episodes.title: Episode 147

episodes.synopsis: Artuk Bey helps Ertuğrul ensnare their enemies as Gümüştekin and Aytolun prepare to realize their ultimate plan.
episodes.title: Episode 148

episodes.synopsis: After Selcan and Banu Çiçek's meeting, Goncagül and Aytolun scramble to cover their tracks. Ertuğrul suspects Saadettin Köpek has a hidden agenda.
episodes.title: Episode 149

episodes.synopsis: Aytolun and Goncagül walk into Ertuğrul's trap. Tuğtekin witnesses a scene that turns the tables on Gümüştekin.
episodes.title: Episode 150

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul reveals the shocking truth to Gündoğdu. As Gümüştekin takes the helm, Hayme and Tuğtekin invite him to a private meeting.
episodes.title: Episode 151

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul becomes Gümüştekin's greatest threat, and Aytolun exploits Tuğtekin's weakness in order to strike at Ertuğrul.
episodes.title: Episode 152

episodes.synopsis: Gümüştekin takes Ertuğrul's bait. With Gündoğdu in critical condition, Selcan and Halime unwittingly put their own lives on the line to find a cure.
episodes.title: Episode 153

episodes.synopsis: After a violent showdown with Selcan, Goncagül is nowhere to be seen. Gümüştekin awaits final judgment.
episodes.title: Episode 154

episodes.synopsis: Saadettin Köpek arrives at the camp to challenge Ertuğrul's authority. Ertuğrul makes new enemies, and an old one returns.
episodes.title: Episode 155

episodes.synopsis: Gökçe reveals a secret to Tuğtekin, and Selcan brings Hayme good news. Ertuğrul's rivals come together to plot revenge.
episodes.title: Episode 156

episodes.synopsis: As the Kayı clan celebrates, news about Gündoğdu's health dampens the mood and another threat looms.
episodes.title: Episode 157

episodes.synopsis: Goncagül finds a partner in crime, and Saadettin Köpek makes her an impossible offer. Yiğit and Dündar become new targets.
episodes.title: Episode 158

episodes.synopsis: As the two clans discuss their next migration, Ertuğrul makes a bold strategic proposal. For Yiğit and Dündar, Noyan is dangerously close.
episodes.title: Episode 159

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul is not the only one with his eye on Byzantine territory, and a rival schemes to pit the two clans against each other.
episodes.title: Episode 160

episodes.synopsis: Saadettin Köpek sets his plan in motion with Noyan's help, and Goncagül plants ideas in Yiğit's head.
episodes.title: Episode 161

episodes.synopsis: Saadettin Köpek deceives Sungur Tekin. Noyan has Yiğit exactly where he wants him, but Turgut may jeopardize the plan.
episodes.title: Episode 162

episodes.synopsis: Saadettin Köpek writes a letter to Sultan Alaeddin and arrives at the camp to show Ertuğrul a package related to Yiğit.
episodes.title: Episode 163

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul and Halime see through Saadettin Köpek's deception. As Noyan prepares for revenge, Gökçe and Tuğtekin fall in harm's way.
episodes.title: Episode 164

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul tries to outrun Noyan's army, and Gündoğdu narrowly escapes a tragic fate. Gökçe's life hangs by a thread.
episodes.title: Episode 165

episodes.synopsis: Saadettin Köpek draws up a new scheme against the Kayı clan, and Sungur Tekin is the key to its success. Tuğtekin tracks down the traitor in the camp.
episodes.title: Episode 166

episodes.synopsis: Halime finds a hidden message in Yiğit's letter. Gökçe takes from Noyan something dear to him.
episodes.title: Episode 167

episodes.synopsis: Yiğit has a trick up his sleeve that plays to Turgut's favor. Noyan exacts revenge against Tuğtekin, while Ertuğrul falls for an enemy's ruse.
episodes.title: Episode 168

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul finds Saadettin Köpek's connection to Noyan. Saadettin Köpek attempts to manipulate Sungur Tekin and turn opinion against Ertuğrul.
episodes.title: Episode 169

episodes.synopsis: Hayme confronts Saadettin Köpek and puts him in a difficult position with Noyan. Saadettin Köpek uses Sungur Tekin to force Ertuğrul's hand.
episodes.title: Episode 170

episodes.synopsis: Saadettin Köpek divides the Kayı family as it suffers another tragic loss. Ertuğrul catches Noyan unawares.
episodes.title: Episode 171

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul makes a controversial decision that pits him against Turgut. Saadettin Köpek rushes to keep Sultan Alaeddin out of reach from Ertuğrul.
episodes.title: Episode 172

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul's decisions divide the camp, and Turgut chooses his own path. Saadettin Köpek puts pressure on Sungur Tekin to fulfill a risky mission.
episodes.title: Episode 173

episodes.synopsis: Hayme struggles to keep peace between Ertuğrul and Gündoğdu as the clans choose a new leader. Sungur Tekin stirs up trouble for Ertuğrul.
episodes.title: Episode 174

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul plays into Saadettin Köpek's hands. A power struggle ensues in the camp as Akça Bey and Saadettin Köpek conspire behind the scenes.
episodes.title: Episode 175

episodes.synopsis: Ahead of the vote, Akça Bey helps Gündoğdu gain political leverage against Ertuğrul. Turgut goes after his own target.
episodes.title: Episode 176

episodes.synopsis: Saadettin Köpek gives Doruk Bey an important task and moves in on Ertuğrul, who has no choice but to leave home base.
episodes.title: Episode 177

episodes.synopsis: Order breaks down in the camp as tensions heat up between Ertuğrul and Akça Bey, but Hayme stands her ground.
episodes.title: Episode 178

episodes.synopsis: Sungur Tekin struggles to talk Hayme out of her final decision. Boğaç Alp and Doruk Bey outnumber Ertuğrul, but underestimate his abilities.
episodes.title: Episode 179

episodes.synopsis: Before fulfilling Sultan Alaeddin's orders, Ertuğrul must find a spy at Hanlı Market. Tensions rise between Banu Çiçek and Halime at the Kayı camp.
episodes.title: Episode 1

episodes.synopsis: Ural Bey's betrayal of his own clan pits him against father Candar Bey and sister Aslıhan, who helps Ertuğrul sell animal pelts at the market.
episodes.title: Episode 2

episodes.synopsis: Back at the Kayı camp, Ertuğrul maps out a plan to rescue Sultan Alaeddin's spy from Hanlı Market. Ural sets his scheme in motion at the Çavdar camp.
episodes.title: Episode 3

episodes.synopsis: After a close shave with Maria, Ertuğrul brings the spy with him and learns the name of an enemy. Ural and Çolpan plan their next treacherous move.
episodes.title: Episode 4

episodes.synopsis: Aliyar finds suspicious traces on Toktamış's body. Ertuğrul sells his rugs at a handsome price to a Venetian buyer -- much to Ural's chagrin.
episodes.title: Episode 5

episodes.synopsis: Maria helps Turgut as his life hangs by a thread. Aliyar finds out about Ural's role in the raid, which threatens Çavdar-Kayı relations.
episodes.title: Episode 6

episodes.synopsis: As Ertuğrul investigates the attack on Turgut's caravan, Aliyar faces a dilemma and Ural schemes to cover his tracks.
episodes.title: Episode 7

episodes.synopsis: As Aliyar sets out for the Kayı camp, two men are ordered to bring the dagger to Ertuğrul, who accepts the Çavdar clan's invitation.
episodes.title: Episode 8

episodes.synopsis: As Simon conspires to pit the Çavdar and Kayı clans against each other, Candar proposes a business partnership with Ertuğrul.
episodes.title: Episode 9

episodes.synopsis: Çolpan tries to stir tensions between Halime and Aslıhan. Turgut declares he's parting ways with Ertuğrul, but Simon is skeptical about his motives.
episodes.title: Episode 10

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul's men set up a trap to mislead the Knights Templar about Sultan Alaeddin's informant. Artuk helps Aliyar investigate Toktamış's death.
episodes.title: Episode 11

episodes.synopsis: Maria and Simon tell Turgut of their personal grudge against the Knights Templar. Simon agrees on a rug deal with Ertuğrul.
episodes.title: Episode 12

episodes.synopsis: Turgut follows Maria to the secret chamber and uncovers a dark truth about Simon. Batuhan and Amanda plot against Halime and Aslıhan.
episodes.title: Episode 13

episodes.synopsis: Bamsi brings Ertuğrul an encrypted note regarding Simon. Aliyar asks his subordinate to track down the maid present on the night of Toktamış's death.
episodes.title: Episode 14

episodes.synopsis: Bamsi's group faces ambush while surveilling Simon and Saadettin Köpek, who's wary of Ertuğrul's plans to conquer Karacahisar.
episodes.title: Episode 15

episodes.synopsis: With Halime and Aslıhan in captivity, Francisco extorts Ertuğrul for gold. Köpek and Ural draw up a dangerous plan against Ertuğrul.
episodes.title: Episode 16

episodes.synopsis: Turgut gains Simon and Maria's trust. Amanda colludes with Ural and tells Aliyar about Francisco's involvement in Halime and Aslıhan's abduction.
episodes.title: Episode 17

episodes.synopsis: After a violent showdown between Ertuğrul and Francisco, Simon appears before Ertuğrul's family with a captive: a witness who might expose Ural.
episodes.title: Episode 18

episodes.synopsis: Simon realizes he's been tricked by Turgut. Ertuğrul frees Amanda and orders his men to follow her, but Ural complicates the plan.
episodes.title: Episode 19

episodes.synopsis: Candar tells Aslıhan about his plan to marry her off. Simon and Maria set up a trap for Turgut in order to kill Ertuğrul.
episodes.title: Episode 20

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul reads Simon's letter and falls gravely ill, making Turgut the main suspect. Simon asks Maria to kill Turgut.
episodes.title: Episode 21

episodes.synopsis: As everyone at the Kayı camp mourns a tragedy, Artuk keeps a secret and asks to take Ertuğrul into a tent alone.
episodes.title: Episode 22

episodes.synopsis: Maria gets a taste of her own poison. As Ertuğrul tries to anticipate Ural's next move, Artuk sends Dündar on a mission and promises him answers.
episodes.title: Episode 23

episodes.synopsis: Ural schemes to take over both clans. Simon vows revenge and Ertuğrul launches a surprise attack at Hanlı Market.
episodes.title: Episode 24

episodes.synopsis: After Ertuğrul takes over Hanlı Market, Ural sets out to find Simon before Turgut does. Candar is troubled by the Kayı family's secrecy.
episodes.title: Episode 25

episodes.synopsis: Artuk Bey links the Knights Templar to Toktamış's death. Ural confronts Simon and promises Saadettin Köpek that he will kill Ertuğrul.
episodes.title: Episode 26

episodes.synopsis: Keen to avoid animosity between the two clans, Ertuğrul faces a dilemma when Candar Bey makes an unexpected proposal.
episodes.title: Episode 27

episodes.synopsis: Torn between Halime and clan politics, Ertuğrul hesitates with Candar's offer and gives Ural an excuse to stir tensions.
episodes.title: Episode 28

episodes.synopsis: Candar beats the war drums and Ural plots to disrupt Hanlı Market trade. Ertuğrul faces ambush during a meeting with Sultan Alaeddin's informant.
episodes.title: Episode 29

episodes.synopsis: Saadettin Köpek interrupts Ertuğrul's assembly of chieftains, and bandits raid the caravan from Constantinople. Aslıhan's bitterness grows.
episodes.title: Episode 30

episodes.synopsis: Tensions rise between Ural and Ertuğrul, who decides to set out for Karacahisar Castle after receiving news of a trade embargo on Hanlı Market.
episodes.title: Episode 31

episodes.synopsis: Ural conspires with Vasilius in a plan to take over Hanlı Market. Artuk Bey asks Kutluca to be Ertuğrul's eyes and ears at the camp.
episodes.title: Episode 32

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul appears before the governor of Karacahisar Castle and falls for Vasilius's trap. Turgut races against time to prove Ertuğrul's innocence.
episodes.title: Episode 33

episodes.synopsis: As Vasilius scrambles to learn of Helena's whereabouts, Ertuğrul and the governor try to identify possible suspects behind the scheme.
episodes.title: Episode 34

episodes.synopsis: Vasilius and his men close in on Ertuğrul as Bamsi and Turgut help Helena find a way into the castle alive. Kutluca eavesdrops on Aybüke and Çolpan.
episodes.title: Episode 35

episodes.synopsis: Kutluca interrogates Aybüke, Aslıhan responds to Saadettin Köpek's unexpected proposal and the governor decides to resume trade with Hanlı Market.
episodes.title: Episode 36

episodes.synopsis: Turgut goes after the culprit as the governor's life hangs by a thread. Saadettin Köpek uses the incident to implicate Ertuğrul.
episodes.title: Episode 37

episodes.synopsis: Aliyar finds evidence on Aybüke, and Turgut traces the governor's killer to Ural, who makes a deal with Byzantine merchant Laskaris.
episodes.title: Episode 38

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul receives news of Saadettin Köpek's plan to take Hanlı Market by force. Petrus overhears Bamsi telling Helena about her father's killer.
episodes.title: Episode 39

episodes.synopsis: Laskaris reveals Ural's treachery to Candar and Saadettin Köpek. Vasilius plans to use Helena to claim power.
episodes.title: Episode 40

episodes.synopsis: Saadettin Köpek attempts to clear Ural's name and promises Vasilius the governor's seat in exchange for peace with the Selçuk state.
episodes.title: Episode 41

episodes.synopsis: Ural and Çolpan's judgment day looms, Vasilius orders Petrus to bring him Ural, and Candar declares Ertuğrul his sworn enemy.
episodes.title: Episode 42

episodes.synopsis: The sultan's magistrate hands down Ural's judgement, and tensions come to a head between Candar and Ertuğrul.
episodes.title: Episode 43

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul is determined to make Aliyar the head of the Çavdar clan, and Vasilius plans to take advantage of the delay in Ural's execution.
episodes.title: Episode 44

episodes.synopsis: Aslıhan turns against Ertuğrul. Vasilius gives Saadettin Köpek evidence to prove Ural's innocence and pin the blame on the Knights Templar.
episodes.title: Episode 45

episodes.synopsis: Aliyar and Aslıhan come to blows over his plan to become clan chief. Batuhan switches sides, and Petrus helps Ural avoid a death sentence.
episodes.title: Episode 46

episodes.synopsis: Pending the selection of the Çavdar chief, Saadettin Köpek convinces Ertuğrul to pardon Ural and maintain peace between the two clans.
episodes.title: Episode 47

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul negotiates with Saadettin Köpek to ensure Aliyar becomes the Çavdar chief, but Saadettin Köpek makes Aslıhan a conflicting promise.
episodes.title: Episode 48

episodes.synopsis: Aslıhan confronts Batuhan, who's determined to tell her the truth about Saadettin Köpek. Helena retrieves from a fireplace a note addressed to Vasilius.
episodes.title: Episode 49

episodes.synopsis: As Aslıhan's whereabouts remain unknown to Saadettin Köpek, Batuhan makes Vasilius an offer that would spell trouble for the Kayı and Çavdar clans.
episodes.title: Episode 50

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul learns about Batuhan's visit to Karacahisar and warns Saadettin Köpek about a scheme involving Aslıhan's abduction.
episodes.title: Episode 51

episodes.synopsis: Aliyar and Ural fall for Batuhan's trap. Vasilius's men lock up Bamsi after he meets with Helena.
episodes.title: Episode 52

episodes.synopsis: Ural plans to seize control at the camp, Ertuğrul's men find Aslıhan's horse, and Vasilius's attempt to negotiate with Saadettin Köpek fails.
episodes.title: Episode 53

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul asks Saadettin Köpek to agree to Vasilius's demands. Helena accepts Vasilius's proposal -- under one condition.
episodes.title: Episode 54

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul and his men trace Aslıhan's whereabouts. Vasilius frees Bamsi -- but sends Teo after him.
episodes.title: Episode 55

episodes.synopsis: During a heated confrontation with Ertuğrul, Vasilius uses Bamsi to ensure his own survival. Saadettin Köpek encounters Ural on his way to Konya.
episodes.title: Episode 56

episodes.synopsis: Vasilius thwarts Ertuğrul's attempts to strengthen alliances with the other chieftains. Ural and Çolpan make an escape plan.
episodes.title: Episode 57

episodes.synopsis: Ural and Çolpan seek an alliance with Vasilius, who's reluctant to partner with them -- until Turgut's group infiltrates Karacahisar.
episodes.title: Episode 58

episodes.synopsis: Helena vows to avenge her father's death and tells Turgut about an important supplies shipment from Nicaea.
episodes.title: Episode 59

episodes.synopsis: Helena leads Turgut's group to a secret escape tunnel. Dündar stirs inter-clan tensions during training.
episodes.title: Episode 60

episodes.synopsis: Ural informs Vasilius of Ertuğrul's plan to intercept the shipment from Nicaea. Vasilius sets out bait in order to identify the spy within.
episodes.title: Episode 61

episodes.synopsis: Halime and Günyeli come to blows, Ertuğrul suspects Yağız's loyalties, and Vasilius prepares to double-cross Ertuğrul.
episodes.title: Episode 62

episodes.synopsis: Çolpan follows Helena to the market and recognizes Haçaturyan. Ertuğrul's group faces off against Teo and his men.
episodes.title: Episode 63

episodes.synopsis: Vasilius hears news of Teo's defeat and Helena's fate hangs in the balance. Ertuğrul sends a package to Karacahisar that turns Vasilius against Ural.
episodes.title: Episode 64

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul expresses concerns to Dündar about his relationship with Günyeli, who gets wind of Dündar's secret mission to Konya.
episodes.title: Episode 65

episodes.synopsis: Amid a scheme to help Teo escape, Aliyar asks Kutluca to closely watch Acar. Peril awaits Doğan and Dündar on the road to Konya.
episodes.title: Episode 66

episodes.synopsis: As the Kayı clan reckons with a tragic loss, Ertuğrul scrambles to find Dündar, while Vasilius sets a trap.
episodes.title: Episode 67

episodes.synopsis: The Byzantine emperor considers war against the Turks and summons Vasilius and Helena to Nicaea. Acar and Günyeli find themselves in dire straits.
episodes.title: Episode 68

episodes.synopsis: Aslıhan extracts a confession from Günyeli. Vasilius's journey to Nicaea allows Ertuğrul an opportunity to strike Karacahisar.
episodes.title: Episode 69

episodes.synopsis: Vasilius encounters an unpleasant surprise on the way to Nicaea and rushes back to Karacahisar, but Ertuğrul is one step ahead.
episodes.title: Episode 70

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul makes inroads at Karacahisar, Helena runs from Vasilius's men, and the Kayı clan's prayers are answered.
episodes.title: Episode 71

episodes.synopsis: As the day of reckoning looms for Teo, Acar and Günyeli, Ural rallies his allies to stage a rebellion against Aliyar and Ertuğrul.
episodes.title: Episode 72

episodes.synopsis: Bamsi and Helena prepare for their nuptials. Vasilius agrees to support Ural's ambitions of power with troop reinforcements.
episodes.title: Episode 73

episodes.synopsis: Ural plants a distraction at the camp so that he can stage an overthrow. Vasilius insists on keeping Çolpan at Karacahisar as leverage against Ural.
episodes.title: Episode 74

episodes.synopsis: During a meeting between Ertuğrul and the chieftains at Hanlı Market, Dündar unexpectedly appears with shocking news.
episodes.title: Episode 75

episodes.synopsis: Ural wreaks havoc back at the camp, Halime's life hangs by a thread, and Vasilius considers breaking his word to Ural.
episodes.title: Episode 76

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul suspects the sultan's spy in Nicaea is in danger. Vasilius waits for the right time to strike.
episodes.title: Episode 77

episodes.synopsis: Halime becomes suspicious of mysterious visitors claiming to be merchants. Vasilius traces the footprints of the sultan's spy.
episodes.title: Episode 78

episodes.synopsis: Dumrul sends a group to follow Ebu Mansur when he suddenly departs Hanlı Market. Ertuğrul and his men fall into a trap.
episodes.title: Episode 79

episodes.synopsis: Vasilius suspects Ebu Mansur is hiding his true identity. Sultan Alaeddin comes across a note and decides that war is inevitable.
episodes.title: Episode 80

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul vows to take Karacahisar and help the sultan guard his borders. Aslıhan grieves as the Kayı family welcomes its newborn son, Savcı.
episodes.title: Episode 81

episodes.synopsis: Saadettin Köpek leaves Hanlı Market in haste for the camp, where Aslıhan tells him that she intends to stay with her clan until she avenges her family.
episodes.title: Episode 82

episodes.synopsis: Saadettin Köpek suspects Aslıhan still harbors affections for Ertuğrul. Çolpan delivers important information to Vasilius.
episodes.title: Episode 83

episodes.synopsis: Saadettin Köpek conspires against Ertuğrul out of jealousy, but Ibn Arabi stands to foil his plot.
episodes.title: Episode 84

episodes.synopsis: Vasilius readies his army and Aslıhan joins the Çavdar clan in challenging Saadettin Köpek, whose scheme unravels.
episodes.title: Episode 85

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul encounters an unexpected obstacle during a decisive face-off with Vasilius's army. The sultan investigates the poisoning incident.
episodes.title: Episode 86

episodes.synopsis: To protect Karacahisar, Çolpan convinces Nikolas to join forces with Saadettin Köpek, who evades the sultan's suspicions.
episodes.title: Episode 87

episodes.synopsis: As Ertuğrul prepares to take over Karacahisar, Çolpan draws up a plan with the Byzantine generals to overcome the Turks.
episodes.title: Episode 88

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul offers Turgut a proposal that would pave the way for a union of the two clans. The Byzantine emperor sends Cmdr. Ares to Karacahisar.
episodes.title: Episode 89

episodes.synopsis: Saadettin Köpek asks the sultan to send Ertuğrul away to battle Mongol forces. Ertuğrul negotiates his terms for peace with Ares.
episodes.title: Episode 90

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul accepts the sultan's mandate to carry out the campaign in the east. Saadettin Köpek writes Çolpan a message that spells trouble for Ertuğrul.
episodes.title: Episode 91

episodes.synopsis: Bamsi's account of the confrontation reaches Saadettin Köpek. The Kayı clan finds an item belonging to Ertuğrul during their search for his traces.
episodes.title: Episode 1

episodes.synopsis: Saadettin Köpek and Ares wait to make their next move, the Kayı clan mourns, and Dündar takes over the reins.
episodes.title: Episode 2

episodes.synopsis: Saadettin Köpek imposes his will on the camp and sends Turgut away. Bahadır sets his sights on the Çavdar clan.
episodes.title: Episode 3

episodes.synopsis: Antheus prepares to deliver Ertuğrul to Simko. Tensions rise between Bahadır and Aslıhan upon his arrival at the camp.
episodes.title: Episode 4

episodes.synopsis: Dündar faces pressure to sell the Hanlı Market, Bahadır challenges Aslıhan's authority, and an unpleasant surprise awaits Simko.
episodes.title: Episode 5

episodes.synopsis: Dündar's decision stirs the clan, Ertuğrul attempts an escape with the other captives, and Ares suspects Marya is Simko's spy.
episodes.title: Episode 6

episodes.synopsis: Ares prepares for war, Bahadır gains control of Hanlı Market, and Ertuğrul wins new allies in his quest to track down his conspirators.
episodes.title: Episode 7

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul and his group face setbacks and Ares presses Marya for information on Antheus. Halime and Artuk defy Dündar's plan.
episodes.title: Episode 8

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul sets out to track down Simko after an ambush, Turgut and Bahadır come to blows, and Marya confronts a tragic reality.
episodes.title: Episode 9

episodes.synopsis: Bahadır threatens to seize control of the clan from Aslıhan. Ertuğrul interrogates a captive about the identity of those who schemed against him.
episodes.title: Episode 10

episodes.synopsis: Dündar's decisions lead to divisions within the Kayı clan. Ares hunts down Simko and grapples with an unpleasant truth.
episodes.title: Episode 11

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul and his men race against the clock to reach Hanlı Market before Dündar signs the momentous deal.
episodes.title: Episode 12

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul punishes Dündar for his rash decisions, the Kayı clan prepares to exact revenge, and Aslıhan curbs Bahadır's quest for power.
episodes.title: Episode 13

episodes.synopsis: Saadettin Köpek's role in the conspiracy against Ertuğrul comes to light. Ares summons a dangerous ally to help him defeat Ertuğrul.
episodes.title: Episode 14

episodes.synopsis: Saadettin Köpek sets out for Konya and gives an order that would endanger Aslıhan. Titan infiltrates the Kayı camp.
episodes.title: Episode 15

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul arrives at Karacahisar, Abdurrahman and Atsız exchange key information, and Gündüz becomes Titan's target.
episodes.title: Episode 16

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul's men prepare to attack Karacahisar. Artuk scrambles to find a cure as Aslıhan and Turgut's fate hangs by a thread.
episodes.title: Episode 17

episodes.synopsis: Bahadır realizes he's been framed and anticipates retribution from Ertuğrul. Ares changes his tack upon receiving Titan's news.
episodes.title: Episode 18

episodes.synopsis: Ares tells Ertuğrul where the poison originated. Saadettin Köpek asks Göktuğ to cover his tracks.
episodes.title: Episode 19

episodes.synopsis: Saadettin Köpek falls out of favor with Sultan Alaeddin. Ares considers making Bahadır a potential ally against Ertuğrul.
episodes.title: Episode 20

episodes.synopsis: Alfonso ingratiates himself with Niko as Ertuğrul prepares for an ambush against Ares's men. Gündüz unwittingly reveals crucial information to Titan.
episodes.title: Episode 21

episodes.synopsis: Gündüz's whereabouts remain unknown, Ertuğrul plans to interrogate Niko, and Saadettin Köpek pins the blame for the sultan's poisoning on Ekaterina.
episodes.title: Episode 22

episodes.synopsis: Saadettin Köpek lays a trap for the sultan, Ertuğrul links Gündüz's kidnapping to Ares, and Bahadır makes another attempt to take over the camp.
episodes.title: Episode 23

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul and Ares scheme to double-cross each other, Turgut faces an ambush, and Marya bonds with Gündüz.
episodes.title: Episode 24

episodes.synopsis: Bahadır avoids suspicion, but he's not out of the woods yet. Atsız confronts Marya, whose true motives come to light.
episodes.title: Episode 25

episodes.synopsis: Ares draws up another scheme. Bahadır accepts Ertuğrul's invitation to the chiefs' gathering at Hanlı Market, but he has a hidden plan.
episodes.title: Episode 26

episodes.synopsis: Both sides make preparations for the imminent war. Atsız discovers what Ares is planning to use to defeat Ertuğrul. Titan extends an offer to Bahadır.
episodes.title: Episode 27

episodes.synopsis: While Ertuğrul and his army head for Karacahisar, a recovered Sancar attempts to overtake the Çavdar camp and Titan ambushes the catapult builders.
episodes.title: Episode 28

episodes.synopsis: Samsa faces off against Titan. Suspecting he's been betrayed, Ertuğrul sends Turgut to the Çavdar camp to find Bahadır and bring him back.
episodes.title: Episode 29

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul tries to recreate from memory Bahadır's catapult blueprints. Ares asks Bahadır to lure Ertuğrul into a trap. Atsız finds a way to escape.
episodes.title: Episode 30

episodes.synopsis: Enraged by Bahadır's invitation, Ertuğrul and his men set off for the Çavdar camp. Atsız races to warn Ertuğrul of Ares' trap before it's too late.
episodes.title: Episode 31

episodes.synopsis: Hearing what happened at the Çavdar camp, Titan scrambles to close the entrance to the   secret passage in time. Hayme assigns new duties to the women.
episodes.title: Episode 32

episodes.synopsis: Those inside Karacahisar's fortress feast and dance, unaware that Ertuğrul is about to launch a stealth attack on them via the secret passageway.
episodes.title: Episode 33

episodes.synopsis: Hoping to escape, Ares hides among the dead. Ertuğrul declares himself ruler of Karacahisar and decides how his Christian subjects will be treated.
episodes.title: Episode 34

episodes.synopsis: Ares and Titan reunite and plan their next step. Marya helps Artuk find an incriminating letter. A messenger from Bilecik delivers an offer to Ertuğrul.
episodes.title: Episode 35

episodes.synopsis: Atsız discovers Titan and Ares' hideout. Turgut puts Aslıhan in her place. Marya is asked if she'll accept a suitor chosen for her.
episodes.title: Episode 36

episodes.synopsis: Hayme tells her son her last wish. Caught eavesdropping on Ares, Atsız flees on horseback to warn Ertuğrul of the plan to kill him at Hanlı Bazaar.
episodes.title: Episode 37

episodes.synopsis: Hayme hovers between life and death. To deflect suspicion away from himself, Saadettin chooses a scapegoat. Ertuğrul and his men head for Hanlı Bazaar.
episodes.title: Episode 38

episodes.synopsis: The sultan declares everyone a suspect and has Nizamettin brought to him. Ertuğrul gains the upper hand over Ares and makes him an offer.
episodes.title: Episode 39

episodes.synopsis: Ares decides whether to accept Ertuğrul's deal. The sultan reveals who his heir will be to Saadettin, who immediately begins scheming with this intel.
episodes.title: Episode 40

episodes.synopsis: Turgut's new role as leader of the Çavdar clan strains his friendship with Bamsi. Saadettin sends a warning to Mahperi about her son's future.
episodes.title: Episode 41

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul investigates Nizamettin's apparent suicide. Hafsa delivers good news to Bamsi. Titan and his contract killers attempt an abduction.
episodes.title: Episode 42

episodes.synopsis: When the sultan returns, Ertuğrul makes a bold accusation and presents Ares to testify. News of the abduction worsens Bamsi and Turgut's relationship.
episodes.title: Episode 43

episodes.synopsis: While in the dungeon together, Saadettin tries to make Ares doubt Ertuğrul's word. Racked with guilt, Turgut sets out alone to find Hafsa and Aslıhan.
episodes.title: Episode 44

episodes.synopsis: Ares has a powerful dream. The sultan announces his decision about Saadettin's fate. Turgut captures Angelos and tries to make him talk.
episodes.title: Episode 45

episodes.synopsis: Saadettin reveals to Mahperi how he plans to kill the sultan. With no better option, Bamsi brings a hooded Ares decoy to the hostage exchange location.
episodes.title: Episode 46

episodes.synopsis: Altun Aba sets in motion a plan to kill Ertuğrul. Aslıhan warns Ertuğrul's men of a mole. Gıyaseddin arrives in Kayseri to join his father's campaign.
episodes.title: Episode 47

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul tries to convince Aziz that arresting him is part of a plan to kill the sultan. Titan and his contract killers launch a raid on Hanlı Bazaar.
episodes.title: Episode 48

episodes.synopsis: The sultan reveals to Gıyaseddin his intentions for his sons' futures. Artuk catches the mole red-handed. Ertuğrul is brought before the sultan.
episodes.title: Episode 49

episodes.synopsis: The Kayı and Çavdar clans clamor for Titan's execution. The sultan's cook fulfills Saadettin's order. Hayme receives a surprise visitor.
episodes.title: Episode 50

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul's men confront an intruder in Karacahisar Castle, who makes a shocking declaration. Mahperi pressures her son to execute Ertuğrul immediately.
episodes.title: Episode 51

episodes.synopsis: Halime and Hayme travel to Konya and confront Mahperi. Ahmet is visited by a shockingly familiar face. Gıyaseddin offers Ertuğrul a deal.
episodes.title: Episode 52

episodes.synopsis: Gıyaseddin demands the truth from his mother. A judgment is passed on Ertuğrul. Sungur Tekin and his men attempt to rescue Turgut, Bamsi and Artuk.
episodes.title: Episode 53

episodes.synopsis: Günalp decides to make an example of Turgut, Bamsi and Artuk. Using his best acting skills, Ahmet tries to take command of Titan's band of assassins.
episodes.title: Episode 54

episodes.synopsis: In a dream, Halime is shown her future child. Ertuğrul announces a migration plan. Artuk receives an urgent message about Prince Kılıçarslan.
episodes.title: Episode 55

episodes.synopsis: Using his former name, Ahmet offers his services to the governor of Bilecik. Kılıçarslan tries to flee from Altun Aba. Artuk visits his wife in prison.
episodes.title: Episode 56

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul realizes what Saadettin's endgame is. Artuk learns Günalp is meeting with the governor of Bilecik. Aslıhan disregards her husband's authority.
episodes.title: Episode 57

episodes.synopsis: After a talk with her son, Mahperi questions her trust in Saadettin. Ertuğrul tries to ease Aslıhan's fears about migrating. Marya gets an offer.
episodes.title: Episode 58

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul sets out to show Günalp who Saadettin really is. To force Gıyaseddin's hand, the emirs threaten to withdraw their support in his war campaign.
episodes.title: Episode 59

episodes.synopsis: Kritos' men are lured into Ertuğrul's trap. Saadettin receives a shocking visitor. When a prediction Ertuğrul makes comes true, Günalp grows uneasy.
episodes.title: Episode 60

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul surrenders his title and castle to Günalp. Marya is given her first mission. The union of the Kayı and Çavdar clans reaches a crossroads.
episodes.title: Episode 61

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul learns of a new threat to the welfare of the state. Aslıhan feels a strong calling to act as an individual for the sake of thousands.
episodes.title: Episode 62

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul tries to dissuade the Oğuz tribesmen from revolting. Aslıhan forces her way into the sultan's palace and demands to see Saadettin.
episodes.title: Episode 63

episodes.synopsis: Gıyaseddin reveals to his mother how he plans to get rid of Saadettin. Aslıhan begs Saadettin for help. Ertuğrul tries to make Günalp see reason.
episodes.title: Episode 64

episodes.synopsis: Mahperi hears the news about Saadettin. Marya listens carefully as Kritos sends Ahmet on a mission. Gıyaseddin secretly meets with the emir of Sivas.
episodes.title: Episode 65

episodes.synopsis: A horrific delivery is made to the Çavdars and Kayıs. Günalp decides to take advantage of the situation and plans a preemptive strike against Ertuğrul.
episodes.title: Episode 66

episodes.synopsis: The emir of Sivas finds his way to Ertuğrul. A recovered Saadettin sets off with his army to conquer Samsat Castle, but gets alarming news on the way.
episodes.title: Episode 67

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul leads an ambush to rescue Emir Kamyeri. Günalp is pressured to take action against the Kayı clan to force Ertuğrul to return. Hafsa falls ill.
episodes.title: Episode 68

episodes.synopsis: The emir of Sivas sets out to win Saadettin's trust. Mahperi offers help for Hafsa. Günalp's first officer seizes an opportunity he's been waiting for.
episodes.title: Episode 69

episodes.synopsis: When Saadettin is finally left alone, Ertuğrul enters his tent, disguised as a messenger. Back at the Kayı camp, Gıyaseddin's life falls into peril.
episodes.title: Episode 70

episodes.synopsis: As Saadettin tortures Ertuğrul to force him to talk, Ertuğrul begs Günalp to open his eyes. Mahperi shares her regrets with Halime and Hayme.
episodes.title: Episode 71

episodes.synopsis: As the emir of Sivas gathers a small army of his most trustworthy men, Ertuğrul plans to lure Saadettin into a trap. Marya becomes suspicious of Ahmet.
episodes.title: Episode 72

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul returns home, where Gıyaseddin restores his title and position. The arrival of a new trader causes a stir at Hanlı Bazaar.
episodes.title: Episode 73

episodes.synopsis: Almıla interrupts a council meeting to report a complaint. A mysterious figure visits Kritos with a warning. Ertuğrul's past comes back to haunt him.
episodes.title: Episode 74

episodes.synopsis: Kritos meets with the stranger who warned him about spies in his household, and vows to go after another target next. Halime gives birth.
episodes.title: Episode 75

episodes.synopsis: Halime hides from her family what she knows to be her fate. After a shocking turn of events, the Kayıs turn to their faith and one another for strength.
episodes.title: Episode 76

episodes.synopsis: Kritos tells Ahmet he plans to attack the tannery, hoping Ahmet takes the bait. Ertuğrul has a fortuitous encounter with a woman grieving her own loss.
episodes.title: Episode 77

episodes.synopsis: The woman Ertuğrul has just met soon attracts danger. Noyan spies Ertuğrul's men setting off for the tannery. Ahmet runs into the cloaked man again.
episodes.title: Episode 78

episodes.synopsis: Sugay is brought to Ertuğrul's home. Noyan gives his sister a new mission, and is told of a premonition. Bilecik's new commander visits the Kayı camp.
episodes.title: Episode 79

episodes.synopsis: Gıyaseddin agrees to Ögedei Khan's request, but makes one of his own in return. Romanos offers the Kayı and Çavdar clans a deal.
episodes.title: Episode 80

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul receives his orders — and a mysterious bag — from Gıyaseddin. Tensions threaten to boil over when Noyan stays the night as Ertuğrul's guest.
episodes.title: Episode 81

episodes.synopsis: On their way to visit Ögedei Khan, Ertuğrul and Noyan are ambushed. Almıla endears herself to Ertuğrul's family. Günalp investigates Almıla's origins.
episodes.title: Episode 82

episodes.synopsis: When Almıla hears Sugay was abducted, she seizes an opportunity to win Günalp's trust. Ertuğrul and his men race to save a critically wounded Bamsi.
episodes.title: Episode 83

episodes.synopsis: Hayme tries to get Sugat to open up about her abductors. Eynece learns Gıyaseddin has sent an important letter to Karacahisar Castle.
episodes.title: Episode 84

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul and his men finally arrive at Ögedei Khan's pavilion. Almıla devises a plan to deflect Günalp's suspicion away from her and Eynece.
episodes.title: Episode 85

episodes.synopsis: Ögedei Khan extends an offer to Ertuğrul, whose response stuns Noyan. A chat with a Turkish defector leads Turgut and Bamsi to a shocking realization.
episodes.title: Episode 86

episodes.synopsis: As a token of gratitude, Hayme gives Almıla a gift, and begins thinking of her as a daughter. Ertuğrul's prayer for a way out of the deal is answered.
episodes.title: Episode 87

episodes.synopsis: When the Mongols posing as messengers from the sultan's palace leave Karacahisar, Günalp secretly follows them. Noyan and his men corner Ertuğrul.
episodes.title: Episode 88

episodes.synopsis: A new face takes a seat on Ögedei Khan's throne. Turgut and Bamsi go to the tannery to confront the infiltrators. An unsuspecting Almıla visits Hayme.
episodes.title: Episode 89

episodes.synopsis: The emperor's son offers Ertuğrul a peace deal. Noyan hears about the tannery and his sister. The Kayı and Çavdar clans prepare to migrate to Söğüt.
episodes.title: Episode 90

episodes.synopsis: More than a decade after the Kayıs conquered and settled in Söğüt, the peace they fought for is disrupted by the delivery of a critically wounded child.
episodes.title: Episode 1

episodes.synopsis: When Ertuğrul learns that moneylenders have set up shop in Hanlı Bazaar, he demands to know who's funding their loans — and is stunned by their reply.
episodes.title: Episode 2

episodes.synopsis: The Mongol commander barges into Ertuğrul's tent and gives a bold order. Hayme urges her son to remarry. İlbilge returns home to her awaiting father.
episodes.title: Episode 3

episodes.synopsis: İlbilge returns to the Kayı camp — this time with her father. An unconscious Ertuğrul awakens to a surprise. Dragos' knight Teo gains access to Teokles.
episodes.title: Episode 4

episodes.synopsis: While Ertuğrul and his men head to Konya to fulfill their new mission, Dragos and his allies sow seeds of discontent among the public at Hanlı Bazaar.
episodes.title: Episode 5

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul first impression of Cmdr. Black Wolf proves to be a horrifying one. Teokles becomes very upset when his daughter Nea reports losing something.
episodes.title: Episode 6

episodes.synopsis: Dragos prepares to secretly incite a war — and make it appear as if Gündüz is to blame. Ertuğrul and his men ambush the Mongols transporting the chest.
episodes.title: Episode 7

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul demands Gündüz reveal where he was coming from when Ataç arrived. Osman and Savcı meet further danger. Turgut and Mergen trick the two spies.
episodes.title: Episode 8

episodes.synopsis: While Ertuğrul rescues his two youngest sons, Dragos encounters his eldest and abducts him. Artuk becomes suspicious of Teokles' medicine.
episodes.title: Episode 9

episodes.synopsis: İlbilge pays the bell ringer for info. Dragos launches his plan to further frame Gündüz. Turgut and Mergen come face to face with the Mongols' top spy.
episodes.title: Episode 10

episodes.synopsis: In the wake of the recent murders, violent chaos breaks out at the inn. Tara demands that Mikis abandon his loyalty to Ertuğrul and join Dragos' side.
episodes.title: Episode 11

episodes.synopsis: Turgut and Mergen overhear their captors discussing what Teokles knew. Ertuğrul tests İlbilge's trust in him. Çağri is followed to Gündüz's hideout.
episodes.title: Episode 12

episodes.synopsis: The bell ringer gives İlbilge info that shatters her trust in Ertuğrul. Dragos' men lie in wait for Ertuğrul to pass northward. Gündüz is cornered.
episodes.title: Episode 13

episodes.synopsis: Evdokya shows Turgut the necklace. Irene sneaks Gündüz into her father's castle. Ertuğrul returns home to find an unexpected visitor waiting for him.
episodes.title: Episode 14

episodes.synopsis: At the castle, Lais forces Mara to reveal where Gündüz is, while Turgut demands that Yannis tell him everything he knows about Dragos and Teokles.
episodes.title: Episode 15

episodes.synopsis: Bahattin summons the bell ringer and gives him a job. Ertuğrul receives two pieces of shocking news from Yannis' castle. İlbilge learns where Gündüz is.
episodes.title: Episode 16

episodes.synopsis: Hayme confides in Hafsa. Gündüz finally gets what he's longed for. İlbilge and Bahattin are stunned when they learn where Ertuğrul is taking his son.
episodes.title: Episode 17

episodes.synopsis: Hayme is visited by someone she hasn't seen in years, but their happy reunion is soon interrupted by Bahattin. Ertuğrul turns the tables on İlbilge.
episodes.title: Episode 18

episodes.synopsis: Hayme's daughter-in-law Selcan hides a secret from the family. Ertuğrul brings his son back to Söğüt to stand trial, along with two witnesses.
episodes.title: Episode 19

episodes.synopsis: Selcan tearfully delivers an encrypted letter and news from home to Ertuğrul, and shares with Hayme an observation about İlbilge.
episodes.title: Episode 20

episodes.synopsis: Dragos, in disguise as the bell ringer, sets out to win the trust of Ertuğrul and his family. Ertuğrul formulates a plan to defeat the Mongols for good.
episodes.title: Episode 21

episodes.synopsis: Beybolat makes a declaration, and demonstrates just how two-faced and bloodthirsty he is. Gündüz visits Irene's tent, but finds only a letter there.
episodes.title: Episode 22

episodes.synopsis: At the border, Ertuğrul confronts Lais and demands to know where the necklace and Dragos are. Beybolat presents a proposal to his sister.
episodes.title: Episode 23

episodes.synopsis: Dragos learns of the plan to deliver the tax collection to Konya. Selcan notices how unhappy İlbilge looks, and tries to get her to open up.
episodes.title: Episode 24

episodes.synopsis: Artuk is abducted. Dragos' men ambush the convoy carrying the tax collection. No sooner does Ertuğrul's special guest arrive than trouble follows.
episodes.title: Episode 25

episodes.synopsis: A man claiming to be Dragos visits Ertuğrul and names his terms for İlbilge's release, but Ertuğrul and Beybolat disagree on what to do next.
episodes.title: Episode 26

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul's men use all their tracking skills to search for Artuk. When Artuk refuses to talk, his captor begins to make good on his threat.
episodes.title: Episode 27

episodes.synopsis: The news about Beybolat reaches both of his sisters. Ertuğrul sets off for Lefke Castle with the ransom — and a trick up his sleeve.
episodes.title: Episode 28

episodes.synopsis: While Turgut and Beybolat try to rescue İlbilge from her captivity in the castle, Ertuğrul risks his life to offer Uranos a tempting deal.
episodes.title: Episode 29

episodes.synopsis: Beybolat invites Ertuğrul to a feast to discuss a "favorable deed" that will seal their tribes' brotherhood. Dragos launches a plan to steal the gold.
episodes.title: Episode 30

episodes.synopsis: Selcan continues to cause discord among the women. Ertuğrul asks İlbilge about a change he's noticed in her. Beybolat's feast takes an unexpected turn.
episodes.title: Episode 31

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul explains to his sons why he's going to remarry. Furious over the theft of the gold, the Mongols come looking for Bahattin.
episodes.title: Episode 32

episodes.synopsis: Turgut leads a raid on the cellar where the gold is being kept. Dragos receives a special delivery. Selcan and Hafsa get into a heated argument.
episodes.title: Episode 33

episodes.synopsis: To avenge the blinding of Artuk and find out who Albastı is, Ertuğrul and his men launch a surprise attack on the Mongols. The poison finds its victim.
episodes.title: Episode 34

episodes.synopsis: Beybolat's life hangs by a thread. Hafsa broaches a difficult subject with her husband. Turgut and Bamsi embark on a mission to form an alliance.
episodes.title: Episode 35

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul meets with the Anatolian leaders, who've become daunted by recent events. Bamsi and Turgut are lured into a trap. Beybolat recruits a new spy.
episodes.title: Episode 36

episodes.synopsis: Beybolat's new spy visits Lefke Castle and offers Uranos a deal in exchange for information. Dragos uses the priest to lead Ertuğrul into an ambush.
episodes.title: Episode 37

episodes.synopsis: The reason for Dragos' intervention is revealed, but his selfless act raises suspicion. The Kayı camp comes under a sudden and massive attack.
episodes.title: Episode 38

episodes.synopsis: Cmdr. Alıncak makes a startling comment about Beybolat. Osman's fury — and bravery — get the better of him. Ertuğrul forges a timely alliance.
episodes.title: Episode 39

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul visits Lefke Castle to try to convince Uranos to ally with him, and learns Osman's life is at stake. Cmdr. Alıncak takes a liking to Sırma.
episodes.title: Episode 40

episodes.synopsis: Alıncak declares Sırma leader of the Kayı women. Ertuğrul arrives at the Kayı camp — but will he hand over the chest? İlbilge receives a secret message.
episodes.title: Episode 41

episodes.synopsis: Osman tries to escape from the Mongols. Mergen intercepts and alters a written order from Hülagü Khan to Alıncak. Selcan refuses to obey Sırma.
episodes.title: Episode 42

episodes.synopsis: At Lefke Castle, Uranos wines and dines Alıncak to get him to reveal where Osman is being held. At the bazaar, Beybolat starts making upsetting changes.
episodes.title: Episode 43

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul and his men try to rescue Osman from the Mongol camp. After Süleyman escapes from the dungeon, İlbilge hides him from those searching for him.
episodes.title: Episode 44

episodes.synopsis: Sırma imposes a restriction on Hayme and Selcan. Osman awakens, but is his memory intact? As promised, Ertuğrul delivers the chest to Alıncak.
episodes.title: Episode 45

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul uses the gold to strike a bargain with Alıncak. When Mergen intercepts Hülagü Khan's next order, a chance to ruin Alıncak's reputation arises.
episodes.title: Episode 46

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul gives the bell ringer instructions to pass on to Dragos at Lefke Castle. The bickering between Sırma and Selcan takes a violent turn.
episodes.title: Episode 47

episodes.synopsis: İlbilge orders that Selcan be arrested and jailed. Certain it was Ertuğrul who sabotaged his mission, Alıncak sets out for the Kayı camp to get revenge.
episodes.title: Episode 48

episodes.synopsis: Dragos realizes Ertuğrul must have a spy who tipped him off about the handover of Keykavus. Beybolat decides to punish Selcan without a trial first.
episodes.title: Episode 49

episodes.synopsis: At Ertuğrul's insistence, Selcan is given a trial, during which İlbilge is forced to testify. Ertuğrul reports to Alıncak — without the gold.
episodes.title: Episode 50

episodes.synopsis: Alıncak's men arrive at the spot where Keykavus is being held. Ertuğrul replaces Beybolat's banners with his own and reclaims his rule over Söğüt.
episodes.title: Episode 51

episodes.synopsis: A defeated Beybolat returns from battle to find his banners gone. Selcan sees her son off on a mission to deliver the letter of pardon to his father.
episodes.title: Episode 52

episodes.synopsis: Sırma accuses her sister of stealing her leadership role. En route to his father, Süleyman encounters trouble. Dragos forces open the chest of secrets.
episodes.title: Episode 53

episodes.synopsis: Uranos returns the broken chest to Ertuğrul, who leverages his guilt. To force him to reveal where the letter of pardon is, Süleyman is tortured.
episodes.title: Episode 54

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul and his men find Süleyman. Alıncak changes tactics and decides to attack Ertuğrul from within, and sets out to identify the spy leaking intel.
episodes.title: Episode 55

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul realizes Albastı must be very close by in order to have known about Süleyman's mission. Mergen is given a message to deliver, but is followed.
episodes.title: Episode 56

episodes.synopsis: Beybolat meets the real Dragos. Ertuğrul warns Uranos that if Mergen isn't rescued soon, Mergen might reveal Hülagü Khan's order to attack Lefke Castle.
episodes.title: Episode 57

episodes.synopsis: Sırma's act of culinary sabotage succeeds in creating a rift between Hafsa and Selcan. In a dream, Osman meets his grandfather Süleyman Shah.
episodes.title: Episode 58

episodes.synopsis: Disguised as Byzantine soldiers, Ertuğrul and his men accompany Uranos to a meeting with Alıncak, whom they hope will lead them to Mergen — and Albastı.
episodes.title: Episode 59

episodes.synopsis: Beybolat realizes Alıncak is a liability and must be dealt with. Selcan notices Sırma is spending a lot of time with Hafsa and becomes suspicious.
episodes.title: Episode 60

episodes.synopsis: Turgut instructs Uranos to use his spy at the inn to lure Alıncak into a trap. Ertuğrul has a stern talk with Bamsi for disobeying an order.
episodes.title: Episode 61

episodes.synopsis: As promised, Uranos hands over the bell ringer to Alıncak. Sırma tries to turn Hafsa against Ertuğrul for punishing her husband.
episodes.title: Episode 62

episodes.synopsis: Alıncak discovers he's walked into a trap and is no longer the hunter, but the prey. Hafsa tries again to convince her husband that they should move.
episodes.title: Episode 63

episodes.synopsis: Mergen is tasked with making Alıncak talk, a job he accepts with great relish. Ertuğrul feeds false intel to the bell ringer.
episodes.title: Episode 64

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul has an inspiring dream. Sırma takes Hafsa and her children to the bazaar as part of a secret plan to turn Hafsa's husband against Ertuğrul.
episodes.title: Episode 65

episodes.synopsis: Dragos' men go to the spot on the map where the gold is supposed to be. İlbilge and Selcan hear the news about Aybars and set out to find him.
episodes.title: Episode 66

episodes.synopsis: Bamsi finds his son — along with a masked man calling himself Albastı. Ertuğrul sends a chest and a message to Lefke Castle.
episodes.title: Episode 67

episodes.synopsis: Hoping to lure Albastı out of hiding, Ertuğrul lets Beybolat and Dragos know that Alıncak is still alive and will be brought to Konya the next day.
episodes.title: Episode 68

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul learns what Bamsi did and sets out to find him before it's too late. Bamsi brings Alıncak to the border to exchange him for his son.
episodes.title: Episode 69

episodes.synopsis: Grief bonds Osman and Selcan. With Dragos in custody, Ertuğrul tests Beybolat to see if he's Albastı. İlbilge spots a familiar scar.
episodes.title: Episode 70

episodes.synopsis: İlbilge asks her brother about the wounded man with the scar. Beybolat devises a plan for Dragos' execution day. Bamsi gets some much-needed counsel.
episodes.title: Episode 71

episodes.synopsis: When Dragos is brought out to be executed, secret plans are set in motion. İlbilge spots the man with the scar sneaking away from the camp.
episodes.title: Episode 72

episodes.synopsis: Artuk does all he can to save Bamsi from his wound. İlbilge hesitates to tell Ertuğrul about the man with the scar, which would implicate her brother.
episodes.title: Episode 73

episodes.synopsis: Sırma forces Mengü to hand over the secret message. Ertuğrul delivers an ultimatum to the emperor's emissary. Bamsi proves to be a bad patient.
episodes.title: Episode 74

episodes.synopsis: Albastı is finally unmasked, confirming İlbilge's worst fear. A long-awaited visitor arrives at the Kayı camp to a joyous welcome.
episodes.title: Episode 75

episodes.synopsis: A new leader of the Umuroğlu tribe is named. Selcan is at last reunited with her husband. Ertuğrul's men spot Beybolat lying along the riverbank.
episodes.title: Episode 76

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul and Gündoğdu recall the last time they were together. A disguised Arıkbuka gives Sırma a message. Mergen brings Berke Khan's envoy to Ertuğrul.
episodes.title: Episode 77

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul and his men are overwhelmed in the ambush led by Arıkbuka. Sırma pressures her sister to marry Ertuğrul as soon as possible.
episodes.title: Episode 78

episodes.synopsis: The terrible news reaches the Kayı and Umuroğlu camps. Arıkbuka demands answers from Ertuğrul. As he hovers between life and death, Turgut has a dream.
episodes.title: Episode 79

episodes.synopsis: Gündüz finds the bloodied fabric that was torn from his father's kaftan. İlbilge insists on joining the search. Ertuğrul attempts a daring escape.
episodes.title: Episode 80

episodes.synopsis: As Gündoğdu and his men walk into Arıkbuka's trap, Ertuğrul races back to the cave before it's too late. İlbilge returns to her camp with a body in tow.
episodes.title: Episode 81

episodes.synopsis: Sırma and Arıkbuka discuss plans for revenge. Bamsi, Gündüz and Günküt go undercover at a caravansary where Mongol spies are known to exchange intel.
episodes.title: Episode 82

episodes.synopsis: Arıkbuka learns Ertuğrul and Gündogdü are embarking on separate missions in different directions. A vote is held to elect İlbilge's successor.
episodes.title: Episode 83

episodes.synopsis: The elected leader of the Umuroğlu tribe announces his first decision. Ertuğrul's men follow Arıkbuka's wounded soldier to Berke Khan's gold shipment.
episodes.title: Episode 84

episodes.synopsis: İlbilge tells Ertuğrul's family of her sister's secret meeting. Gündoğdu gets word from brother Sungur Tekin. Arıkbuka conspires with Berke Khan's spy.
episodes.title: Episode 85

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul asks Berke Khan for permission to bait his closest confidant to prove he's a spy. İlbilge and Turgut deliver the traitors to the Umuroğlu camp.
episodes.title: Episode 86

episodes.synopsis: When Kıyat steals intel from Berke Khan's tent, Ertuğrul must stop it from reaching Hülagü Khan. Sırma fakes remorse and plots to kill her sister.
episodes.title: Episode 87

episodes.synopsis: Ertuğrul and his men return to the Kayı camp, which immediately begins to bustle with preparations for a wedding — and a sendoff of the soldiers to war.
episodes.title: Episode 88
